profile: Centra Windows is headquartered in Langley BC, with a state of the art manufacturing facility producing the high-quality, energy-efficient vinyl windows. We’ve been in business for over 35 years and with our employees also being our owners – we take pride in the work that we do. We are the industry leaders and are always ahead of our competitors with our products, technology, and service. Visit us in one of our branch locations across BC in: Langley, Victoria, Nanaimo, or Kelowna.

profile: We specialize in replacement windows, doors and patio doors for the residential market and work directly with homeowners, and take care of supplying and installing the windows and doors. We offer energy efficient vinyl windows, steel and fibreglass doors and patio doors. Our window options include casement, awning, slider, hung, bay, bow, shape and combination windows. Our windows and doors available with triple-pane glass on all our models including slider and hung windows. We offer financing options, and have our own dedicated installers. After the installation we dispose of your old windows and doors. All our windows and doors come with product and installation warranty. Our mission is to improve your home!

profile:
Doctor Screen is the Doctor that makes house calls to fix your screen doors. You will no longer have to go to the trouble to arrange that yourself! We do it all onsite. 

We offer many solutions for all of your screening needs. Solar Screens,Patio Shades, Sliding Screen Doors and many other items. We can do screens that do not disturb your view as well as screens that offer privacy in your home or on your patio. From a job as simple as a window or door re-screen to something as big as a new screen porch or screened enclosure, give us a call. We can repair or replace all screens. We are your screen experts.

profile:
NEW TOWN LTD
New Town Ltd is a spearheading glass installation and renovation company proudly serving businesses and families across Okanagan Valley. Established on a core foundation of integrity, trust, and authenticity, CEO Harison Pyykko and his team take pride in leveraging their collected 25+ years of experience within the industry and coming together to not only meet customer expectations, but exceed them every time.


We're social here: 
https://www.facebook.com/NewTownGlass/
https://twitter.com/NewTownGlass

https://newtownglass.ca/
https://newtownwindows.ca/
 

Developed with humble beginnings right here in Kelowna, the creative professionals at New Town Glass, Ltd have illuminated their expertise and supported the brand to become the leading glass repair and installation company that you see today. Overall, they have a deeply rooted passion for their work and demonstrate their devotion by delivering qualified, professional, and innovation-driven services, all while featuring a strong commitment to provide a positive and seamless experience for every customer.

 

Nothing makes the fully licensed and insured New Town Glass team happier than being a valuable resource for commercial and residential glass needs and raising the standards bar along the way. From showers, engineered interior and exterior railings, glass office cubicles, glass backsplashes, commercial curtain walls and doors, and much more, you can have the solidifying confidence that your project objectives are in the best possible hands from start to finish.

OUR STATEMENT
New Town Glass and its people are committed to providing quality products and service, where our customers are confident they have made the right choice.

We are pleased to serve a variety of clients, including:

Home Owners
Home Builders
Renovation Contractors
Architectual Engineers
Commercial Designers
Interior Designers
Residential and Commercial Developers
